Description: Include cstdint in V8 base/macros.h
 Newer libstdc++/compiler combinations no longer expose fixed-width integer
 types transitively through the existing V8 base includes. Include cstdint
 directly in macros.h.
Author: Dockershelf Maintainers <41898282+github-actions[bot]@users.noreply.github.com>
Forwarded: no

--- a/deps/v8/src/base/macros.h
+++ b/deps/v8/src/base/macros.h
@@ -7,6 +7,7 @@
 
 #include <limits>
 #include <type_traits>
+#include <cstdint>
 
 #include "src/base/compiler-specific.h"
 #include "src/base/logging.h"
